                    <p>The purpose of this article is to investigate the intuition and evidence that underpin various investment techniques, as well as to provide a strategy for accessing these sources of returns within a framework that is liquid and market-neutral. </p>
                    <p>We are of the opinion that designs have the potential to fulfill the requirements of a large number of investors by offering a source of returns that is for the most part untouched by conventional risk factors, while also providing diversification into traditional alternatives. With the advent of market-neutral daily liquidity strategies, investors may have access to an additional instrument that provides them with the opportunity to achieve their return objectives.</p>
